headline: Dow completes $150MM sale of flexible packaging laminating adhesives business
summary: Dow (NYSE: DOW) announced today the completion of its previously announced sale of the Company's flexible packaging laminating adhesives business, within Dow's Packaging & Specialty Plastics segment, for $150 million to Arkema, a specialty materials leader.
